<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.9.1">
<l>peṭaiyaṭartta maṭavaṉṉam piriyātu malarkkamalam</l>
<l>maṭaleṭuttu matunukarum vayaluṭutta tirunaṟaiyūr</l>
<l>muṭaiyaṭartta ciramēnti mūvulakum palitirivōṉ</l>
<l>iṭarkeṭutta tiruvāḷa ṉiṇaiyaṭiyē yaṭaineñcē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In Tirunaṟaiyūr surrounded by fields where a simple swan,</l>
<l rend="indent">which had clung to its mate,</l>
<l>Never leaving, taking the petal of a blossoming lotus, relished the nectar,</l>
<l>O heart, take refuge at both feet of the one who is Tiru’s lord</l>
<l rend="indent">who removed the distress</l>
<l>Of the one who wandered the three worlds [begging] for alms,</l>
<l rend="indent">bearing a skull where flesh clung.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
